{"tid":1267550,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"烈士？有部分係你地成就","createTime":"2019-06-30T02:53:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T10:34:40.000Z","uid":166199,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ff5ae310bcef2639002eade23bb65761ab31c8e6","tid":1267550,"uid":166199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T02:53:53.000Z","msg":"你地係咁講 吹捧 ，好似一死就成為烈士<br />\n又話好傷心又剩 比咁大認同感佢地<br />\n<br />\n比左好大誘因 個d唔識諗既人 做傻事<br />\n要知道香港有好多人要睇精神科<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇緊既你 要知道事隔數年除左家人 仲有邊個記你地<br />\n上連登匆太認真"},{"pid":"00e58d4d1590fc8c3dcdff89f5b7ac8ea9a018f6","tid":1267550,"uid":5680,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T02:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q0ZPb75.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ0ZPb75.gif&h=7d8cb952&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc4106995f4039a221e668d15b37838b5fc1d358","tid":1267550,"uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T02:55:50.000Z","msg":"連登仔最多咪俾正皮支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"784dc6a696db5378692758a1fa6b9b72f346080e","tid":1267550,"uid":260312,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:17:30.000Z","msg":"以前連登可能係一個抑鬱症病人嘅舒壓地方<br />\n全部都係玩下玩下 睇完真係好舒壓<br />\n依家全部討論政治 我都明白依家係關乎香港存亡<br />\n但係睇耐咗真係會有種壓力感<br />\n<br />\n所以如果控制唔到自己情緒嘅或者本身諗嘢負面嘅可以休息下 少上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1290ee1622ba1b7a696c17983a97b1f706ecd94b","tid":1267550,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:55:32.000Z","msg":"咪撚戇鳩<br />\n烈士係應該獲得極大尊重<br />\n但唔代表鼓勵人學 咪扭曲概念"},{"pid":"2aab6a0fc92f35e35b8b1401257492f937e29d0f","tid":1267550,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T11:58:50.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"a66469a42ba71d740124c253f738f0bfa48d9496","tid":1267550,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T12:04:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"015640dff971a529da54277f0dbe0f4cb5ff0b75","tid":1267550,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T01:50:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00b71d2962aebad8432d0059c8a8c63a4a0c40ab","tid":1267550,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T10:34:40.000Z","msg":"推"}]}